@startuml
title MunchOut Application - Data Flow Sequence Diagram

actor Customer
actor Restaurant
participant "Flutter UI\n(Views)" as UI
participant "AuthBloc" as AuthBloc
participant "LoginBloc" as LoginBloc
participant "SignupBloc" as SignupBloc
participant "Restaurant\nBLoC" as RestaurantBloc
participant "Customer\nBLoC" as CustomerBloc
participant "UserRepository" as UserRepo
participant "RestaurantRepository" as RestaurantRepo
participant "CustomerRepository" as CustomerRepo
participant "FlaskAPI" as API
database "Flask Backend\n(REST API)" as Backend
database "Database\n(SQLAlchemy)" as DB

== Customer Authentication Flow ==
Customer -> UI: Open App
UI -> AuthBloc: Check Auth Status
AuthBloc -> UserRepo: Get Current User
UserRepo -> API: Request User Session
API -> Backend: GET /user/session
Backend -> DB: Query User
DB --> Backend: User Data
Backend --> API: User Response
API --> UserRepo: User Object
UserRepo --> AuthBloc: Authentication State
AuthBloc --> UI: Unauthenticated

Customer -> UI: Enter Login Credentials
UI -> LoginBloc: Submit Login
LoginBloc -> UserRepo: Login(email, password)
UserRepo -> API: POST /login
API -> Backend: POST /customer/login
Backend -> DB: Validate Credentials
DB --> Backend: Customer Record
Backend --> API: Auth Token + Customer Data
API --> UserRepo: User Session
UserRepo --> LoginBloc: Login Success
LoginBloc -> AuthBloc: User Authenticated
AuthBloc --> UI: Navigate to Customer Home

== Customer Event Booking Flow ==
Customer -> UI: Browse Events
UI -> CustomerBloc: Load Events
CustomerBloc -> CustomerRepo: Get All Events
CustomerRepo -> API: GET /events
API -> Backend: GET /events
Backend -> DB: Query Available Events
DB --> Backend: Event List
Backend --> API: Events JSON
API --> CustomerRepo: Event Objects
CustomerRepo --> CustomerBloc: Events List
CustomerBloc --> UI: Display Events

Customer -> UI: Select Event & Book
UI -> CustomerBloc: Create Booking
CustomerBloc -> CustomerRepo: Book Event(eventId, customerId)
CustomerRepo -> API: POST /booking
API -> Backend: POST /booking
Backend -> DB: Create Booking Record
DB --> Backend: Booking Saved
Backend --> API: Booking Confirmation
API --> CustomerRepo: Booking Object
CustomerRepo --> CustomerBloc: Booking Success
CustomerBloc --> UI: Show Confirmation

Customer -> UI: View My Bookings
UI -> CustomerBloc: Get Customer Bookings
CustomerBloc -> CustomerRepo: Get Bookings(customerId)
CustomerRepo -> API: GET /customer/{id}/bookings
API -> Backend: GET /customer/{id}/bookings
Backend -> DB: Query Customer Bookings
DB --> Backend: Booking List
Backend --> API: Bookings JSON
API --> CustomerRepo: Booking Objects
CustomerRepo --> CustomerBloc: Bookings List
CustomerBloc --> UI: Display Bookings

== Restaurant Authentication Flow ==
Restaurant -> UI: Open App
UI -> AuthBloc: Check Auth Status
AuthBloc -> UserRepo: Get Current User
UserRepo --> AuthBloc: Unauthenticated

Restaurant -> UI: Enter Signup Details
UI -> SignupBloc: Submit Restaurant Signup
SignupBloc -> UserRepo: Register Restaurant(details)
UserRepo -> API: POST /signup
API -> Backend: POST /restaurant/signup
Backend -> DB: Create Restaurant Record
DB --> Backend: Restaurant Saved
Backend --> API: Auth Token + Restaurant Data
API --> UserRepo: User Session
UserRepo --> SignupBloc: Signup Success
SignupBloc -> AuthBloc: User Authenticated
AuthBloc --> UI: Navigate to Restaurant Home

== Restaurant Event Management Flow ==
Restaurant -> UI: View My Events
UI -> RestaurantBloc: Load Restaurant Events
RestaurantBloc -> RestaurantRepo: Get Events(restaurantId)
RestaurantRepo -> API: GET /restaurant/{id}/events
API -> Backend: GET /restaurant/{id}/events
Backend -> DB: Query Restaurant Events
DB --> Backend: Event List
Backend --> API: Events JSON
API --> RestaurantRepo: Event Objects
RestaurantRepo --> RestaurantBloc: Events List
RestaurantBloc --> UI: Display Events

Restaurant -> UI: Create New Event
UI -> RestaurantBloc: Submit Event Details
RestaurantBloc -> RestaurantRepo: Create Event(eventData)
RestaurantRepo -> API: POST /event
API -> Backend: POST /event
Backend -> DB: Insert Event Record
DB --> Backend: Event Saved
Backend --> API: Event Created
API --> RestaurantRepo: Event Object
RestaurantRepo --> RestaurantBloc: Event Success
RestaurantBloc --> UI: Show Event Created

Restaurant -> UI: View Event Bookings
UI -> RestaurantBloc: Get Event Bookings
RestaurantBloc -> RestaurantRepo: Get Bookings(eventId)
RestaurantRepo -> API: GET /event/{id}/bookings
API -> Backend: GET /event/{id}/bookings
Backend -> DB: Query Event Bookings
DB --> Backend: Booking List
Backend --> API: Bookings JSON
API --> RestaurantRepo: Booking Objects
RestaurantRepo --> RestaurantBloc: Bookings List
RestaurantBloc --> UI: Display Bookings

@enduml
